OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773668256
OL,3,CDomestic abuse survivor welcomes a
OL,4,CBill to reduce the right to a jury
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FA survivor of domestic violence has
OL,8,Fwelcomed a Bill to reduce the right to
OL,9,Fa jury trial to help speed up the
OL,10,Flegal process.
OL,12,FKatie Catt's partner started attacking
OL,13,Fher just three months after they met,
OL,14,Fbut she had to wait over a decade
OL,15,Funtil he was found guilty of a series
OL,16,Fof charges.
OL,18,FShe said: "I feel like the court was
OL,19,Fin his favour through the delays.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773668256
OL,3,CDomestic abuse survivor welcomes a
OL,4,CBill to reduce the right to a jury
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,F"He wanted it to go to a jury trial
OL,8,Fbecause for him he wanted to see me,
OL,9,Fquestion me and put me through hell
OL,10,Fand back - like he did for all those
OL,11,Fyears."
OL,13,FKatie said the court wasn't equipped
OL,14,Ffor the victims: "It's there for the
OL,15,Foffenders and that's what needs to
OL,16,Fchange."
OL,18,FThe government's answer to the delays
OL,19,Fis to take away the right to have some
OL,20,Ftrials listened to by a jury.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773668256
OL,3,CDomestic abuse survivor welcomes a
OL,4,CBill to reduce the right to a jury
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FMPs will scrutinise a Bill which could
OL,8,Fsee only the most serious cases
OL,9,Fdecided by a group of 12 men and women.
OL,11,FIt would affect cases with a likely
OL,12,Fsentence of three years; such as
OL,13,Fsexual assault, grievous bodily harm
OL,14,Fand theft.
OL,16,FThe shake up would also take away
OL,17,Fjuries for complex or lengthy cases
OL,18,Flike fraud, when it is in the public
OL,19,Finterest.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773668256
OL,3,CDomestic abuse survivor welcomes a
OL,4,CBill to reduce the right to a jury
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FThe most serious cases, such as
OL,8,Fmurder, would still be heard by juries.
OL,10,FKatie brought four rape charges, three
OL,11,Fcharges of sexual assault and one
OL,12,Fcontrolling and coercive behaviour
OL,13,Fcharge against her former partner.
OL,15,FThe long wait for a trial put her at
OL,16,Fgreater risk.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773668256
OL,3,CDomestic abuse survivor welcomes a
OL,4,CBill to reduce the right to a jury
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FShe said: "For us, as victims of
OL,8,Fdomestic violence, the longer you
OL,9,Fleave it for us to go to court, the
OL,10,Fmore chance we're going to go back to
OL,11,Fthem.
OL,13,F"Because that's what they make us do.
OL,15,F"Where it took so long to get to my
OL,16,Ftrial, I kept going back.
OL,18,F"He kept convincing me that he was
OL,19,Fgoing to change and things would get
OL,20,Fbetter. That never happened."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773668256
OL,3,CDomestic abuse survivor welcomes a
OL,4,CBill to reduce the right to a jury
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FHer ex-partner was eventually
OL,8,Fsentenced to four years in prison.
OL,10,FThe process to get there shattered
OL,11,FKatie's mental health and cost her a
OL,12,Fcareer in property development that
OL,13,Fshe spent 20 years building.
OL,15,FJustice secretary, David Lammy used
OL,16,FKatie's experiences to reinforce his
OL,17,Fargument for reducing the right to a
OL,18,Fjury trial.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773668256
OL,3,CDomestic abuse survivor welcomes a
OL,4,CBill to reduce the right to a jury
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FHe said: "Her life fell apart in that
OL,8,Fperiod, it left her mental health in
OL,9,Ftatters, it caused her to lose her job.
OL,11,F"This is an injustice, it's Katie's
OL,12,Finjustice."
OL,14,FNot everyone is in support of the
OL,15,Fmotion.
OL,17,FThe UK legal reform charity, JUSTICE,
OL,18,Fthinks the root of the issue starts
OL,19,Fbefore a jury even sees the trial.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773668256
OL,3,CDomestic abuse survivor welcomes a
OL,4,CBill to reduce the right to a jury
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FChief Executive, Fiona Rutherford,
OL,8,Ftold ITV News London: "Nearly three
OL,9,Fout of five trials don't make their
OL,10,Fway to the jury in the first place.
OL,12,F"Either through inefficiency, through
OL,13,Fthe case not being ready, through the
OL,14,Flawyers not being available.
OL,16,F"All sorts of issues need to be dealt
OL,17,Fwith before the jury even sees the
OL,18,Ftrial in the first place. Juries are
OL,19,Fnot the problem."
OL,21,FShe said earlier issues arise, adding:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773668256
OL,3,CDomestic abuse survivor welcomes a
OL,4,CBill to reduce the right to a jury
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,F"We know that prison van contracts are
OL,8,Fnot being properly managed, so they're
OL,9,Foften late to court.
OL,11,F"Court buildings themselves are quite
OL,12,Fliterally falling down in real time.
OL,13,FInvestment has just been woeful in the
OL,14,Flast year or so."
OL,16,FFiona argues that jury trials are a
OL,17,Fhistorical and reliable system, adding:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773668256
OL,3,CDomestic abuse survivor welcomes a
OL,4,CBill to reduce the right to a jury
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,F"They are the route in for the public
OL,8,Fto the criminal justice system. Its
OL,9,Fthe most trusted way that we have in
OL,10,Forder to make decisions that can
OL,11,Faffect peoples lives."
OL,13,FBut for Katie, reducing jury trials
OL,14,Foffers hope that fighting for justice
OL,15,Fdoesn't leave victims hurt further.
OL,17,F"All the cases that are coming up, I
OL,18,Fthink offenders are working the system
OL,19,Fso that their cases are delaying the
OL,20,Fwhole process.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773668256
OL,3,CDomestic abuse survivor welcomes a
OL,4,CBill to reduce the right to a jury
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,F"And that's why this is going to help,
OL,8,Fhopefully, the delay.
OL,10,F"You have to relay everything, your
OL,11,Fstory goes over and over again and its
OL,12,Fdraining physically and mentally.
OL,14,F"So I think its a positive step
OL,15,Fforwards to take out the cases that
OL,16,Foffenders are dictating because that's
OL,17,Fwhat's happening.
OL,19,F"Put it back in the power of the court
OL,20,Fsystem and the victims."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
